Default attachment folder for non-Excalidraw binary assets (images, PDFs) pasted or dragged
into notes. Set as Obsidian's default attachment location in Settings > Files & Links.

Excalidraw diagrams do NOT belong here — see ../Excalidraw/Excalidraw Index.md.

If this folder grows large with binary assets over time, consider Git LFS for it specifically
(see ../00-Meta/Git Integration.md).
